#Lucene and HSQL DB

Create an application that uses Lucene Index for fast search and HSQL for In memory DB.

Initialize the Lucene Index Writer for each table in the database and the relationships 
Customer Table --> create Customer Lucene Index file. /Bitset Directory
Order Table --> Create Order Lucene Index File. /Bitset Directory
Create Index File for Customer-Order Records. /Relation Directory

Store the Index Objects in HiperSql-In Memory as Blob data. http://javapapers.com/core-java/serialize-de-serialize-java-object-from-database/

When searching for an order 
1. Get the appropriate index Object from the Hsql
2. Query the index get the ID. 
3. Hit the database and get the Real Object. 


